.seal {
  position: fixed;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 300px;
  height: 300px;
  opacity: 0.05;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  z-index: -1;
}
opacity: 0.05 → makes it faint.

position: fixed → stays behind content even on scroll.

transform: translate(-50%, -50%) → centers the seal perfectly.